<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- lwlạ ạlṣlyb mn ạ̉nạ yạ sydy
 lwlạk yạ fạdy ḥyạty mn ạ̉kwn
 lwlạk knt tạỷhaⁿạ fy ẓlmty
 wkạn qlby gẖạrqaⁿạ tḥt ạldywn
 ạlqrạr- (fạ̉nạ lk wlgẖyrk ln ạ̉kwn)2
 wlạ̉jlk kl tḍḥyẗiⁿ thwn
 (lys mtẖlk mn yḥbny bfw̉ạdh ạlḥnwn)2
 2- lwlạ ạ̹ntẓạry lmjyỷk ạlqryb
 lwlạ rjạỷy fy ḥyạty fy ạlsmạʾ
 lʿsẖt ṭwl ạlʿmr fy kẖwfiⁿ mdẖyb
 mn ạlgẖd ạlmjhwl fy lyl ạlsẖqạʾ
 3- ạ̉kwn fy ạldnyạ srạbaⁿạ ynthy
 ạ̹n knt qd ḥrmt mn ạ̉mjạdk
 mwlạy ạ̉sẖkr ạ̹mtyạzk ạldẖy
 qd ḍmny wạkẖtạrny lbytk</lyrics>
<title>lwlạ ạlṣlyb</title>
